---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-3">
      <Icon name="lucide:user" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" />
      About Me
    </h3>
    <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
      I'm a web developer who builds fast, reliable, and modern web applications
      using frameworks like SvelteKit, Next.js, Astro.js, and FastAPI. I work
      across the full stack — from crafting responsive UIs to designing backend
      APIs, integrating headless CMSs like Strapi and Sanity, and wiring up AI
      services like OpenAI. I've shipped e-commerce platforms, industrial
      websites, bilingual (EN/FA) apps, and production-grade REST APIs. My goal
      is to turn real-world requirements into clean, performant, and maintainable
      solutions — whether that's a pixel-perfect static site or a data-driven
      full-stack application.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
